   <refsect2>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1f0f8567c1257eecf431870f6ba0c2b9 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <title>Semi-Internal Options</title>
________________________________________________________-->
    <title>半内部选项</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1f0f8567c1257eecf431870f6ba0c2b9 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ff20370af33ad41229f8e486e07a14ac sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <para>
     The options described here are used
     mainly for debugging purposes, and in some cases to assist with
     recovery of severely damaged databases. There should be no reason
     to use them in a production database setup.  They are listed
     here only for use by <productname>PostgreSQL</productname>
     system developers.  Furthermore, these options might
     change or be removed in a future release without notice.
    </para>
________________________________________________________-->
    <para>
     这里描述的选项主要被用于调试目的，并且在某些情况下可以协助恢复严重受损的数据库。在生产数据库环境中应该不会去使用它们。在这里列举它们只是为了让<productname>PostgreSQL</productname>系统开发者使用。此外，这些选项可能在将来的版本中更改或删除而不另行通知。
    </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ff20370af33ad41229f8e486e07a14ac -->

    <variablelist>
     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-f</option> <literal>{ s | i | o | b | t | n | m | h }</literal></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=7839ee8c65383ab14490a98bc8bc4dbf sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Forbids the use of particular scan and join methods:
        <literal>s</literal> and <literal>i</literal>
        disable sequential and index scans respectively,
        <literal>o</literal>, <literal>b</literal> and <literal>t</literal>
        disable index-only scans, bitmap index scans, and TID scans
        respectively, while
        <literal>n</literal>, <literal>m</literal>, and <literal>h</literal>
        disable nested-loop, merge and hash joins respectively.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        禁止某种扫描和连接方法的使用：<literal>s</literal>和<literal>i</literal>分别禁用顺序和索引扫描， <literal>o</literal>、<literal>b</literal>和<literal>t</literal>分别禁用只用索引扫描、位图索引扫描以及 TID 扫描，而<literal>n</literal>、<literal>m</literal>和<literal>h</literal>则分别禁用嵌套循环、归并和哈希连接。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=7839ee8c65383ab14490a98bc8bc4dbf -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=67ec3f630a28a63329d531ee6deddbc1 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Neither sequential scans nor nested-loop joins can be disabled
        completely; the <literal>-fs</literal> and
        <literal>-fn</literal> options simply discourage the optimizer
        from using those plan types if it has any other alternative.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        顺序扫描和嵌套循环连接都不可能完全被禁用。<literal>-fs</literal>和<literal>-fn</literal>选项仅仅是在有其他选择时不鼓励优化器使用这些计划类型。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=67ec3f630a28a63329d531ee6deddbc1 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-n</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=97e1e193c9090471dfc76ce3020c9f42 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        This option is for debugging problems that cause a server
        process to die abnormally.  The ordinary strategy in this
        situation is to notify all other server processes that they
        must terminate and then reinitialize the shared memory and
        semaphores.  This is because an errant server process could
        have corrupted some shared state before terminating.  This
        option specifies that <command>postgres</command> will
        not reinitialize shared data structures.  A knowledgeable
        system programmer can then use a debugger to examine shared
        memory and semaphore state.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        该选项主要用于调试导致服务器进程异常崩溃的问题。对付这种情况的一般策略是通知所有其它服务器进程，让它们终止并且接着重新初始化共享内存和信号量。这是因为一个错误的服务器进程可能在终止之前就已经对共享状态造成了破坏。该选项指定<command>postgres</command>将不会重新初始化共享数据结构。一个有经验的系统程序员这时就可以使用调试器检查共享内存和信号量状态。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=97e1e193c9090471dfc76ce3020c9f42 -->
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-O</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e16bab361f59a4a43de8683102163f17 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Allows the structure of system tables to be modified.  This is
        used by <command>initdb</command>.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        允许修改系统表的结构。这个选项用于<command>initdb</command>。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e16bab361f59a4a43de8683102163f17 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-P</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=76cd1c5fcb470db4b015ada9465988d6 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Ignore system indexes when reading system tables, but still update
        the indexes when modifying the tables.  This is useful when
        recovering from damaged system indexes.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        读取系统表时忽略系统索引（但在更改系统表时仍然更新索引）。这在从损坏的系统索引中恢复时有用。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=76cd1c5fcb470db4b015ada9465988d6 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-t</option> <literal>pa[rser] | pl[anner] | e[xecutor]</literal></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=c3bbe285eeb860a848d584600a12f10e sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Print timing statistics for each query relating to each of the
        major system modules.  This option cannot be used together
        with the <option>-s</option> option.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        打印与每个主要系统模块相关的查询的时间统计。这个选项不能和<option>-s</option>选项一起使用。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=c3bbe285eeb860a848d584600a12f10e -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-T</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=bace8b559601cce926604751a49be613 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        This option is for debugging problems that cause a server
        process to die abnormally.  The ordinary strategy in this
        situation is to notify all other server processes that they
        must terminate and then reinitialize the shared memory and
        semaphores.  This is because an errant server process could
        have corrupted some shared state before terminating.  This
        option specifies that <command>postgres</command> will
        stop all other server processes by sending the signal
        <literal>SIGSTOP</literal>, but will not cause them to
        terminate.  This permits system programmers to collect core
        dumps from all server processes by hand.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        该选项主要用于调试导致服务器进程异常崩溃的问题。对付这种情况的一般策略是通知所有其它服务器进程，让它们终止并且接着重新初始化共享内存和信号量。这是因为一个错误的服务器进程可能在终止之前就已经对共享状态造成了破坏。该选项指定<command>postgres</command>将通过发送<literal>SIGSTOP</literal>信号停止其他所有服务器进程，但是并不让它们终止。这样就允许系统程序员手动从所有服务器进程收集内核转储。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=bace8b559601cce926604751a49be613 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-v</option> <replaceable class="parameter">protocol</replaceable></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=a7054bd09be2569c254ccd9d732ceca7 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Specifies the version number of the frontend/backend protocol
        to be used for a particular session.  This option is for
        internal use only.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        声明这次会话使用的前/后服务器协议的版本数。该选项仅在内部使用。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=a7054bd09be2569c254ccd9d732ceca7 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-W</option> <replaceable class="parameter">seconds</replaceable></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=f1da04a26fdeb8705ea2863bdc75efdd sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        A delay of this many seconds occurs when a new server process
        is started, after it conducts the authentication procedure.
        This is intended to give an opportunity to attach to the
        server process with a debugger.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在一个新服务器进程被启动时，它实施认证过程之后会延迟这个选项所设置的秒数。这就留出了机会来用一个调试器附着在服务器进程上。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=f1da04a26fdeb8705ea2863bdc75efdd -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
   </refsect2>

   <refsect2>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=444c7f1232672712f812bf52366aea4b sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <title>Options for Single-User Mode</title>
________________________________________________________-->
    <title>用于单用户模式的选项</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=444c7f1232672712f812bf52366aea4b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b71af08e4011c61c405a7b5035f76495 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <indexterm>
     <primary>single-user mode</primary>
    </indexterm>
________________________________________________________-->
    <indexterm>
     <primary>单用户模式</primary>
    </indexterm>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b71af08e4011c61c405a7b5035f76495 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=48f1792a4431e485896470a7f1f36e49 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
    <para>
     The following options only apply to the single-user mode
     (see <xref linkend="app-postgres-single-user"/> below).
    </para>
________________________________________________________-->
    <para>
     下面的选项仅适用于单用户模式（见<xref linkend="app-postgres-single-user"/>）。
    </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=48f1792a4431e485896470a7f1f36e49 -->

    <variablelist>
     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>--single</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=33a8e1b68aeefed1456da9a2cfec3fc1 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Selects the single-user mode.  This must be the first argument
        on the command line.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        选择单用户模式。这必须是命令行中的第一个选项。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=33a8e1b68aeefed1456da9a2cfec3fc1 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><replaceable class="parameter">database</replaceable></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4ce1476bfc63e92f1e8092224508bcf6 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Specifies the name of the database to be accessed.  This must be
        the last argument on the command line.  If it is
        omitted it defaults to the user name.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        指定要访问的数据库的名称。这必须是命令行中的最后一个参数。如果省略它，则默认为用户名。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4ce1476bfc63e92f1e8092224508bcf6 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-E</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4d62ca2c33820815898152f1fc8b6f5e sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Echo all commands to standard output before executing them.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在执行命令之前回显所有命令到标准输出。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4d62ca2c33820815898152f1fc8b6f5e -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-j</option></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9b302706ab1c9daee40f6263f20de3a4 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Use semicolon followed by two newlines, rather than just newline,
        as the command entry terminator.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        使用跟着两个新行的分号而不是仅用新行作为命令终止符。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9b302706ab1c9daee40f6263f20de3a4 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>

     <varlistentry>
      <term><option>-r</option> <replaceable class="parameter">filename</replaceable></term>
      <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=075012c8f383907a26463f654b01f869 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
       <para>
        Send all server log output to <replaceable
        class="parameter">filename</replaceable>.  This option is only
        honored when supplied as a command-line option.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        将所有服务器日志输出发送到<replaceable class="parameter">filename</replaceable>中。
        只有在作为一个命令行选项提供时，这个选项才会兑现。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=075012c8f383907a26463f654b01f869 -->
      </listitem>
     </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
   </refsect2>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3b1cdb4e9f7c411322dc1c76ca7f31f3 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Environment</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>环境</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3b1cdb4e9f7c411322dc1c76ca7f31f3 -->

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term><envar>PGCLIENTENCODING</envar></term>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3cd2b5ef58aafdb98b5a344359a36c63 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
     <para>
      Default character encoding used by clients.  (The clients can
      override this individually.)  This value can also be set in the
      configuration file.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      客户端使用的默认字符编码（客户端可以独立地覆盖它）。这个值也可以在配置文件中设置。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3cd2b5ef58aafdb98b5a344359a36c63 -->
    </listitem>
   </varlistentry>

   <varlistentry>
    <term><envar>PGDATA</envar></term>

    <listitem>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=3130a9d5974039952cdf70530f917296 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
     <para>
      Default data directory location
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      默认的数据目录位置。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3130a9d5974039952cdf70530f917296 -->
    </listitem>
